# server.cjs IS the deployed entrypoint: this project builds as a Node server,
# so Vercel runs server.cjs and only falls through to it for /api/* (the static
# routes in vercel.json resolve to files before reaching it). It must bind
# 0.0.0.0 in a container or the platform proxy cannot reach it.

# CI-only and non-web assets. The server requires optimizer-core.cjs, core/,
# optimizer-system.cjs and request-guard.cjs, so those must stay deployed.
tests/
extensions/
scripts/
.github/
*.zip
design-qa.md
